---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sponsors | Cloud Identity Summit</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 font-sans antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 flex items-center justify-between h-16">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">CIS</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Cloud Identity Summit</span>
            </a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition">2026</a>
                <a href="/team" class="hover:text-white transition">Team</a>
                <a href="/sponsors" class="text-blue-400">Sponsors</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        <div class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">Our Partners</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-16">Sponsors</h1>
        
        <!-- Gold Sponsors -->
        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Gold Sponsors</h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">adesso SE</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Business success is the result of innovative ideas, forward-looking strategies and perfectly tailored IT solutions. With a team of around 6.300 employees on 56 sites, we are one of the leading IT service providers in the German-speaking area.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">E.ON Digital Technology GmbH</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">E.ON leads the way and takes responsibility. Our mission is nothing less than to be the playmaker of the energy transition in Germany and to make it feasible for everyone.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">glueckkanja AG</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">glueckkanja, a renowned Cloud Managed Service Provider, is a Microsoft partner offering comprehensive cloud solutions. With a unified blueprint approach, glueckkanja uses Infrastructure as Code to transition and support customer infrastructures.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">TOKEN2</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Token2 is a cybersecurity company specializing in multifactor authentication. Alongside legacy OTP-based hardware tokens and standard FIDO2 keys, Token2 offers the innovative PIN+ series.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Silver Sponsors -->
        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Silver Sponsors</h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Omada GmbH</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Omada Identity Cloud is a next-generation IGA-as-a-service platform designed to deliver complete visibility and control over your identity landscape.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">SoftwareCentral | Tenant Manager</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">SoftwareCentral’s Tenant Manager enhances Microsoft Intune with enterprise-grade governance, automates change controls, and delivers granular oversight across multi-tenant environments.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Bronze Sponsors -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Bronze Sponsors</h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">MSC - CyberGuard GmbH</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">As a trusted partner in the field of information security, we are committed to providing companies with comprehensive support and protection.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">water IT Security GmbH</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">water is a cybersecurity company delivering holistic IT security to protect your business. We help you defend against evolving threats through expert consulting and 24/7 monitoring.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">BuildClouds</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-900 bg-slate-950 py-10 mt-auto">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
            © 2026 Cloud Identity Summit
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>